### Article API Examples
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles

### 1. Create a new article (Basic)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse",
  "slogan": "Ergonomic wireless mouse with 6 buttons",
  "netPrice": 15.00,
  "salesPrice": 29.99,
  "vatRatio": 0.19
}

### 2. Create an article with discounts (Non-overlapping)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "slogan": "RGB backlit mechanical gaming keyboard",
  "netPrice": 50.00,
  "salesPrice": 120.00,
  "vatRatio": 0.19,
  "discounts": [
    {
      "description": "Spring Sale",
      "discountPercentage": 20,
      "startDate": "2026-03-01",
      "endDate": "2026-03-31"
    },
    {
      "description": "Summer Sale",
      "discountPercentage": 25,
      "startDate": "2026-06-01",
      "endDate": "2026-06-30"
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Create an article with a single discount
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Hub",
  "slogan": "7-in-1 USB-C multiport adapter",
  "netPrice": 20.00,
  "salesPrice": 49.99,
  "vatRatio": 0.19,
  "discounts": [
    {
      "description": "Black Friday",
      "discountPercentage": 30,
      "startDate": "2026-11-27",
      "endDate": "2026-11-30"
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Get all articles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get article by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1
Accept: application/json

### 6. Update an article (replace {id} with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse Pro",
  "slogan": "Updated ergonomic wireless mouse with 8 buttons",
  "netPrice": 15.00,
  "salesPrice": 34.99,
  "vatRatio": 0.19
}

### 7. Update article and add discount
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse Pro",
  "slogan": "Premium wireless mouse",
  "netPrice": 15.00,
  "salesPrice": 39.99,
  "vatRatio": 0.19,
  "discounts": [
    {
      "description": "Launch Discount",
      "discountPercentage": 15,
      "startDate": "2026-02-01",
      "endDate": "2026-02-28"
    }
  ]
}

### 8. Delete an article (replace {id} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1

### 9. Check if article exists (HEAD request)
HEAD http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1

