### 12. Get non-existent article (Should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/999999
Accept: application/json

### 13. Update non-existent article (Should return 404)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/999999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Non-existent",
  "slogan": "This should fail",
  "netPrice": 10.00,
  "salesPrice": 20.00,
  "vatRatio": 0.19
}

### 14. Delete non-existent article (Should return 404)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/999999
